<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The Night Circus by Erin Morganstern had a similar magical-realism feel and similar lush, evocative prose. Also, if you haven&apos;t read American Gods (Ne<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The Night Circus by Erin Morganstern had a similar magical-realism feel and similar lush, evocative prose. Also, if you haven't read American Gods (Neil Gaiman), I'd definitely recommend that too!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
